		"Name": "Panther",
		"Details": "A Panther jointly developed between Wakizashi Enterprises and Ashlain Weaponry, the Panther PNT-11LB and its sibling PNT-11LD were developed to serve both the Free Rasalhague Republic and the Draconic Combine.  Both variants were faster than the then standard PNT-10 Panther and both were armed with an Lulabin  Autocannon in lieu of the ER PPC.  In the case of the 11LB it is the LB 5-X. All of this lead to a mech who had great staying power thanks to an impressive three tons of ammunition.   Of course conversely 3 tons, even CASE protected makes the mech have a high likelihood of explosion.",
